{"tid":2341207,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"做調查做到成為人民公敵-1937年蘇聯人口普查","createTime":"2020-12-26T07:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T05:55:23.000Z","uid":352783,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"420ffad28174389d6213d91b14b6d4144b4fb4e7","tid":2341207,"uid":352783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:00:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">背景</span></strong><br />\n蘇聯、中國、北韓全部都喺獨立後經歷過大饑荒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係，高層選擇忽略呢D事實，唔俾呢一二百萬嘅「死亡數字」阻礙佢哋執行的偉大理想<br />\n去到問題浮現，就左冚右冚當冇事，埋下更大災難嘅禍根<br />\n1937年蘇聯人口普查，正正就係咁樣一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AqHcfHV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAqHcfHV.jpg&h=3bc91900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該次人口普查嘅宣傳"},{"pid":"ed366c9ad28fe2a7e0f0d0eff0179d71dec9e7eb","tid":2341207,"uid":352783,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">一再拖延嘅人口普查</span></strong><br />\n話說喺事情發生五年前嘅1932年3月，蘇聯開始籌備第二次人口普查，計劃喺第二年進行一次全國性嘅人口普查<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但喺，計劃一再延遲，由33年12月一直拖到36年先搞，最後分包膠係喺37年1月先出到街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解會咁？因為調查期間發生咗一件大事，令到人口普查好難完成。<br />\n<br />\n呢件事就係三十年代初嘅蘇聯大饑荒。"},{"pid":"fc5c1205548f3643e3f6f409989e92d2a85f7833","tid":2341207,"uid":5150,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:24:56.000Z","msg":"lm等學嘢"},{"pid":"63e8ff62f3728c5d0bae4487c5195e48769967ad","tid":2341207,"uid":352783,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:48:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">蘇聯32-34年大饑荒</span></strong><br />\n<strong>背景</strong><br />\n雖然烏克蘭平原係著名嘅黑土大糧倉，土地肥沃農作物產量高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但嗰度偶爾都會因為天氣反常而出現失收，進而導致饑荒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係，同1921年嘅情況唔同，嗰次饑荒係由高速工業及城市化、農作物收成低同國內穀物被大量輸出至國外引致。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能有人會問工業化同饑荒有乜關係，試諗下，冚世界去哂工廠打工冇人落田邊度嚟飯你食？<br />\n其實佢哋諗住蘇聯工業化嘅時候農業技術都可以嚟個大躍進以滿足龐大的食物需要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但因為集體化將太多農民趕咗去工廠所以令到D田冇人耕，結果農作物產量就下降，而去工廠嘅工人都要食飯，咁樣就形成咗惡性循環，加劇糧食危機。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFor example,由28年至37年，鋼鐵產量提高咗339%，但同期糖產量只係升咗89%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74d55effc0fb1cf009fd2d5309a7b1422684f7a","tid":2341207,"uid":73854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"068de181e9bb1dc2adb8c71bef1b6d1584e9805b","tid":2341207,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:52:31.000Z","msg":"好像第一次人口普查<br />\n<br />\n統計學家話人口跌左  <br />\n不符合史達林個意思<br />\n<br />\n所以被人殺左<br />\n<br />\n第二次做人口上升"},{"pid":"771b88533b4f589eccf2a27d017bd813399a34e4","tid":2341207,"uid":352783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:23:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><strong>蘇聯32-34年大饑荒</strong></span><br />\n<strong>阻礙居民撤離</strong><br />\n由於擔心受災地區居民逃亡，蘇聯政府要求各大加盟共和國喺關口設卡，只準有證件嘅人放行，而農村居民冇權拎身份證，咁就變相將佢哋禁足，違反命令擅自離開村莊嘅人就古拉格見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然係咁，但仍然有少量農村居民成功逃到大城市(例如基輔、哈爾科夫等)，但因為佢哋冇身份證所以去到都只可以乞食。<br />\n另外，火車都停運防止流民移動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bCr4Zj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bCr4Zj.jpg&h=85625aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1933年哈爾科夫街頭，餓殍遍地而路人彷彿已經習慣咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>受災範圍</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eCLEFxi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeCLEFxi.jpg&h=d88a4a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖中顏色越深，代表受災越嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n可以見到烏克蘭南部、俄羅斯南部、高加索地區、哈薩克受災嚴重，諷刺嘅係呢D地區其實係東歐糧倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>死亡人數</strong><br />\n全蘇聯計，死亡人數由150-700萬人不等，受災最嚴重嘅烏克蘭，死亡人數可能達到500萬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TM992O7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTM992O7.png&h=d4a7b42e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1932年蘇聯西南部人口減少圖<br />\n<br />\n第二嚴重嘅哈薩克，死亡人數150萬人，哈薩克族喺嗰次饑荒受災嚴重，當地人口重新洗牌，該族人口比例甚至比俄羅斯族超越，直到上世紀末先反超返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90FEFBJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90FEFBJ.png&h=8906cfe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁嚴重嘅人口流失，自然影響到當時進行緊嘅人口普查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2175ac9681c64778d569597c30d0265c2fe97616","tid":2341207,"uid":352783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"771b88533b4f589eccf2a27d017bd813399a34e4","tid":2341207,"uid":352783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:23:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><strong>蘇聯32-34年大饑荒</strong></span><br />\n<strong>阻礙居民撤離</strong><br />\n由於擔心受災地區居民逃亡，蘇聯政府要求各大加盟共和國喺關口設卡，只準有證件嘅人放行，而農村居民冇權拎身份證，咁就變相將佢哋禁足，違反命令擅自離開村莊嘅人就古拉格見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然係咁，但仍然有少量農村居民成功逃到大城市(例如基輔、哈爾科夫等)，但因為佢哋冇身份證所以去到都只可以乞食。<br />\n另外，火車都停運防止流民移動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bCr4Zj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bCr4Zj.jpg&h=85625aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1933年哈爾科夫街頭，餓殍遍地而路人彷彿已經習慣咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>受災範圍</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eCLEFxi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeCLEFxi.jpg&h=d88a4a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖中顏色越深，代表受災越嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n可以見到烏克蘭南部、俄羅斯南部、高加索地區、哈薩克受災嚴重，諷刺嘅係呢D地區其實係東歐糧倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>死亡人數</strong><br />\n全蘇聯計，死亡人數由150-700萬人不等，受災最嚴重嘅烏克蘭，死亡人數可能達到500萬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TM992O7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTM992O7.png&h=d4a7b42e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1932年蘇聯西南部人口減少圖<br />\n<br />\n第二嚴重嘅哈薩克，死亡人數150萬人，哈薩克族喺嗰次饑荒受災嚴重，當地人口重新洗牌，該族人口比例甚至比俄羅斯族超越，直到上世紀末先反超返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90FEFBJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90FEFBJ.png&h=8906cfe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁嚴重嘅人口流失，自然影響到當時進行緊嘅人口普查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"題外話:<br />\n第二幅圖白色嗰啲地區當時係波蘭領土，唔係由蘇聯國土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e24478ea93e959d0bdfa7c59601e1348f57e641","tid":2341207,"uid":352783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:26:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span class=\"large\"><strong>蘇聯32-34年大饑荒</strong></span><br />\n<strong>阻礙居民撤離</strong><br />\n由於擔心受災地區居民逃亡，蘇聯政府要求各大加盟共和國喺關口設卡，只準有證件嘅人放行，而農村居民冇權拎身份證，咁就變相將佢哋禁足，違反命令擅自離開村莊嘅人就古拉格見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然係咁，但仍然有少量農村居民成功逃到大城市(例如基輔、哈爾科夫等)，但因為佢哋冇身份證所以去到都只可以乞食。<br />\n另外，火車都停運防止流民移動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bCr4Zj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bCr4Zj.jpg&h=85625aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1933年哈爾科夫街頭，餓殍遍地而路人彷彿已經習慣咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>受災範圍</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eCLEFxi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeCLEFxi.jpg&h=d88a4a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖中顏色越深，代表受災越嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n可以見到烏克蘭南部、俄羅斯南部、高加索地區、哈薩克受災嚴重，諷刺嘅係呢D地區其實係東歐糧倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>死亡人數</strong><br />\n全蘇聯計，死亡人數由150-700萬人不等，受災最嚴重嘅烏克蘭，死亡人數可能達到500萬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TM992O7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTM992O7.png&h=d4a7b42e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1932年蘇聯西南部人口減少圖<br />\n<br />\n第二嚴重嘅哈薩克，死亡人數150萬人，哈薩克族喺嗰次饑荒受災嚴重，當地人口重新洗牌，該族人口比例甚至比俄羅斯族超越，直到上世紀末先反超返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90FEFBJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90FEFBJ.png&h=8906cfe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁嚴重嘅人口流失，自然影響到當時進行緊嘅人口普查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>題外話:<br />\n第三幅圖白色嗰啲地區當時係波蘭領土，唔係由蘇聯國土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"28b819c2501a71e54eda8d2fda8f54f076db330d","tid":2341207,"uid":352783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:42:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">蘇聯高層對人口普查嘅高度期望</span></strong><br />\n喺1934年2月嘅布爾什維克第十七次黨大會，史大林發表報告，話蘇聯人口由1930年年尾嘅1.605億升到33年年尾有1.68億。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1935年2月，佢再喺同集體農莊負責人開會時提到，話蘇聯每年增長當時一個芬蘭嘅總人口(註:1930年芬蘭人口346萬)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根據上述統計，蘇聯官方except總人口會升到1.8億<br />\n另外佢哋根據當時出生同死亡率統計，估計人口會升到1.7-1.72億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d888d5c209c6bec0011c80b8c7d21876df5165e","tid":2341207,"uid":352783,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><strong>調查結果同調查員嘅下場</strong></span><br />\n1937年1月4日(同日為儒略曆平安夜)，調查結果終於出爐，佢哋得出當時人口為1.62億，比十年前嘅調查上升1500萬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d2oKR1z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd2oKR1z.jpg&h=b17e8ee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1937年報告嘅人口金字塔<br />\n<br />\n但係，蘇聯高層對呢個結果唔滿意，即刻將嗰次調查當國家機密鎖起佢，仲要求重做一次調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於嗰一次負責調查嘅官員，一年內全部被拘捕並槍決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1938年7月27日嘅《真理報》社論話：<br />\n「人民公敵misleading普查員，導致大規模人口低估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然而喺勇敢嘅內務人民委員部員尼古拉&middot;葉若夫領導下，將呢D毒蛇消滅喺統計機關的巢穴中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n(編按:呢位葉若夫同志之後喺1940年遭到政治清算被處決)<br />\n<br />\n至於後來1939年嘅調查，左拉右拉終於凑夠1.7億人口嘅目標，再下一次蘇聯有人口調查已經係1959年嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec5a9a2d20333c5fd95e0584c2b4290dce9155a","tid":2341207,"uid":299134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T09:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6e149499797c7561ed1af699099c20e14989f2","tid":2341207,"uid":352783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0ec5a9a2d20333c5fd95e0584c2b4290dce9155a","tid":2341207,"uid":299134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T09:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086fd2ba8df34779a027dddc97413d927b92e745","tid":2341207,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"398ad72bdee1c5e7c4acf6a07ec490ed1c7d6f84","tid":2341207,"uid":352783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T09:39:19.000Z","msg":"要講嘅已經講曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位可以安心服用<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf761793605a9c81f469e74b23c351687f55c9a","tid":2341207,"uid":352783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T09:46:52.000Z","msg":"題外話:<br />\n部分做呢次調查嘅人員，喺1957年被平反<br />\n不過好大可能係「去史大林化」嘅影響，未必代表官方重新認可佢哋當時嘅調查報告<br />\n亦都有人質疑嗰一次人口普查本身就唔科學，攞大時大節做人口普查cut off唔會準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e852bffd8b693a86a5d13f4a59302545c94e7fce","tid":2341207,"uid":38218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T09:47:32.000Z","msg":"Mr. Jones 套電影就係揭露當年呢段歷史"},{"pid":"fea37356d8089122e7a4496829ae54884d420d94","tid":2341207,"uid":106641,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"大規模饑荒真係紅色政權嘅特色嚟"},{"pid":"11c97257f88cc61c59e8d38ade8ec2e1afd4569d","tid":2341207,"uid":352783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fea37356d8089122e7a4496829ae54884d420d94","tid":2341207,"uid":106641,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"大規模饑荒真係紅色政權嘅特色嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T12:35:27.000Z","msg":"Majority係，但都有exceptional cases嘅&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n古巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e59b254ca5a32109a9ca4baa20acdaa4b093f93","tid":2341207,"uid":13343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fea37356d8089122e7a4496829ae54884d420d94","tid":2341207,"uid":106641,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"大規模饑荒真係紅色政權嘅特色嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T16:46:42.000Z","msg":"仲有作大人口嚟增加自己同人showhand/引人落搭嘅籌碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac2ee5bbce661cb6d68601172ff9e41f7504315","tid":2341207,"uid":15830,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fea37356d8089122e7a4496829ae54884d420d94","tid":2341207,"uid":106641,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"大規模饑荒真係紅色政權嘅特色嚟"},"citedBy":0,"r